### Smart Task - TaskController API Test
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Auth
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Dynamic IDs
@projectId = REPLACE_PROJECT_ID
@taskId = REPLACE_TASK_ID
@statusId = REPLACE_STATUS_ID_OR_NULL
@assigneeUserId = REPLACE_ASSIGNEE_USER_ID
@labelId = REPLACE_LABEL_ID

### 1) Create task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Implement login screen",
  "description": "Flutter login + validation",
  "priority": "high",
  "deadline": "2026-03-30T10:00:00",
  "statusId": null,
  "assigneeIds": ["{{assigneeUserId}}"],
  "labelIds": ["{{labelId}}"]
}

### 2) List tasks by project
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3) Update task (title/priority/deadline/assignees/labels)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Implement login + register screens",
  "priority": "medium",
  "deadline": "2026-04-01T17:00:00",
  "assigneeIds": ["{{assigneeUserId}}"],
  "labelIds": ["{{labelId}}"]
}

### 4) Delete task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
